    <item>
      <title>日本大米价格上涨问题在收获后仍将继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/japan-s-struggle-with-rice-inflation-to-continue-after-harvest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着农民收获新作物，预计日本超市的货架上将再次堆满大米，但供应量的增加对于抑制价格上涨作用不大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/japan-s-struggle-with-rice-inflation-to-continue-after-harvest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受美联储加息影响的日本央行计划重返政府债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/japan-bank-stung-by-fed-hikes-plots-return-to-government-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家在日本人口最稀少地区运营的银行正在做一件可能产生全球影响的事情（如果其同行也这么做的话）：这家银行计划在利率上升之际大规模重返日本债券市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/japan-bank-stung-by-fed-hikes-plots-return-to-government-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
